Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Sets whether the player can talk to this character or not. The 'idleAnim' is used when switching to TALK\_OK, it will be the animation to play when not talking. If none is given the anim specified in the "anim" key/value will be used.

Usage
-----

*void* setTalkState( "float" "talkState")

Parameters
----------

-   none

